metadata.name: Bowl Cut Redemption
metadata.description:
The second Open Edition from FroggyCyborg

"The Bowl Cut Redemption," a heartfelt tribute to Elmo and his remarkable transformation into the beloved 'Bowl Cut' penguin. This art piece not only encapsulates Elmo's inspiring journey but also serves as a means to extend our support and appreciation.

It is with great pleasure that we announce that 100% of the proceeds from this exclusive artwork will be dedicated to Elmo himself, acknowledging his invaluable contributions and ensuring his continued success.
